comments: Jackson (LAC) makes contact with the ball and he deflects the pass away from Ayton (PHX).
Batum (LAC) legally contests Crowder's (PHX) jump shot attempt.
Bridges (PHX) maintains a legal guarding position on Jackson (LAC) during his dribble.
Jackson (LAC) maintains a legal guarding position on Booker (PHX) during the drive.
Jackson (LAC) legally contests Booker's (PHX) jump shot attempt.
Booker (PHX) legally contests George's (LAC) jump shot attempt.
Prior to the jump shot attempt, Jackson (LAC) takes fewer than three steps after he has gathered the ball.
Johnson (PHX) legally contests Mann's (LAC) jump shot attempt.

Crowder (PHX) reaches in and places his right hand on the ball as his left hand simultaneously makes marginal contact to George's (LAC) arm during his driving shot attempt. Bridges (PHX) makes contact with the ball.
Mann (LAC) commits a take foul on Booker (PHX).
